type: TS LF Trading Bot Error - Amount Received Node Missing

definition.text: An Amount Received node was expected but not found at the node where the error originated.

translations.text: Alınan Tutar düğümü ( Amount Received ) bekleniyordu ancak hatanın kaynaklandığı düğümde bulunamadı.
Ein Amount Received -Knoten wurde erwartet, aber nicht an dem Knoten gefunden, an dem der Fehler auftrat.
Alınan Düğüm Tutarı Eksik. ( Amount Received Node Missing )
Amount Received -Knoten fehlt (Amount Received Node Missing)

paragraphs.text: Add the missing node and try again.

translations.text: Fügen Sie den fehlenden Knoten hinzu und versuchen Sie es erneut.
